snippet.title: Series Makers Release Trailer - 22.02.2019
snippet.description:
Available on Friday, 22nd of February: https://store.steampowered.com/app/594040/SERIES_MAKERS/

As an apology for the long delay, Series Makers will release with a 40% discount for just 3,59€!
